
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Interactive Waste Flashcards</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --plastic-color: #FF6B6B;
            --paper-color: #4ECDC4;
            --food-color: #45B7D1;
            --electronic-color: #96CEB4;
            --glass-color: #FFEEAD;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c2e59c, #64b3f4);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .page {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100vh;
            transition: transform 0.6s ease-in-out;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .input-page {
            transform: translateX(0);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c2e59c, #64b3f4);
        }

        .cards-page {
            transform: translateX(100%);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #96c93d, #00b09b);
        }

        .show-cards .input-page {
            transform: translateX(-100%);
        }

        .show-cards .cards-page {
            transform: translateX(0);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            animation: floating 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes floating {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }

        .input-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            animation: slideUp 0.6s ease forwards;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            to { transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        select, input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: white;
        }

        select:focus, input:focus {
            border-color: #64b3f4;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(100,179,244,0.2);
            outline: none;
        }

        .submit-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #64b3f4, #96c93d);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .submit-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .flashcards-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .flashcard {
            height: 400px;
            perspective: 1000px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .flashcard-inner {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.8s;
            transform-style: preserve-3d;
        }

        .flashcard.flipped .flashcard-inner {
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
        }

        .flashcard-front, .flashcard-back {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            backface-visibility: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        }

        .flashcard-back {
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
            background: white;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }

        .fact {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .nav-buttons {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 2rem;
            right: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .nav-btn {
            background: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .progress-bar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #64b3f4, #96c93d);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .flashcards-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar"></div>

    <div class="page input-page" id="inputPage">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>‚ôªÔ∏è Waste Awareness Flashcards</h1>
                <p>Learn about environmental impact through interactive cards</p>
            </div>

            <div class="input-container">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label for="waste-type">Select Waste Type</label>
                    <select id="waste-type">
                        <option value="">Choose a waste type...</option>
                        <option value="plastic">Plastic Waste</option>
                        <option value="paper">Paper Waste</option>
                        <option value="food">Food Waste</option>
                        <option value="electronic">Electronic Waste</option>
                        <option value="glass">Glass Waste</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <button class="submit-btn" onclick="showFlashcards()">Create Flashcards</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page cards-page" id="cardsPage">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1 id="cardTitle">Your Flashcards</h1>
            </div>
            <div id="flashcards" class="flashcards-container"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-buttons">
            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="goBack()">‚Ü©Ô∏è</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="shuffleCards()">üîÑ</button>
        </div>
    </div>

